dcterms:description: This dataset includes EEG recordings from 14 schizophrenia patients and 14 healthy controls, recorded while the participants' eyes were closed for a period of 15 minutes, with a sampling rate of 250Hz.
dcterms:title: Schizophrenia (SZ) Dataset

dcterms:description: This dataset consists of EEG recordings from 34 major depressive disorder patients and 30 healthy controls, recorded during a 5-minute eye-closed resting-state EEG session, with a sampling rate of 256 Hz.
dcterms:title: Major Depressive Disorder (MDD) Dataset
